{"tid":1783041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊聖誕同倒數活動  我有建議","createTime":"2019-12-14T12:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-15T04:19:18.000Z","uid":114281,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6838e082af7bd38da6de285b938dba8ff4f2101b","tid":1783041,"uid":114281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:53:57.000Z","msg":"記唔記得早前條街一多人   突然間支那人唔撚見哂<br />\n鑑於見到聖誕開始多支那人一車車嚟香港，有以下建議：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 事前大大力宣傳   瘋狂文宣   一齊<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">行街</span></span><br />\n啲大陸閪咁撚怕事應該唔撚敢嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2.要感受氣氛就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">自己果區</span></span>好啦  度度都咁熱鬧啲腦殘藍絲應該都唔撚夠膽出嚟<br />\n諗住一區半區冇事出嚟買野？收皮啦留係屋企啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n3.行完 飯都要食野架    就去振興埋<span style=\"color: gold;\">黃色經濟</span><br />\n黃店就唔好罷啦 我地都要食野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你知啦   聖誕旺季  藍店收撚哂皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黃店又可以繼續食住個勢唔會被影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最緊要係個城市乾淨咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d82ae70cc53467086047bce7b791fd369c0fb9bd","tid":1783041,"uid":62270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:54:31.000Z","msg":"冇時間啦25號截止，極度要人幫手!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1782422\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1782422</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4434aeececcb024b1c4d87e6c0e7987a72a94a81","tid":1783041,"uid":251769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-14T12:55:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請各位喺出post前貼多張日程表or文宣</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">咁文宣組就冇咁忙啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<img src=\"